Ping gives information like number of packets transmitted, numbe of packets received, % of packet loss, time to respond etc.
In my case, the following is the command and the additional output printed on screen
command : ping 15.207.22.175 -c 4
--- 15.207.22.175 ping statistics ---
4 packets transmitted, 4 received, 0% packet loss, time 3005ms
rtt min/avg/max/mdev = 31.118/42.035/61.843/11.738 ms